@startuml
title LayerStack Reverse Propagation and handled Stop
skinparam shadowing false

participant Application
participant "Overlay Layer" as Overlay
participant "Editor Layer" as Editor
participant "Core Layer" as Core

Application -> Overlay : OnEvent(event)
Overlay --> Application : handled? false
Application -> Editor : OnEvent(event)
Editor --> Application : handled? true
Application -> Core : (skipped)

note right of Application
Propagation stops after handled=true.
end note

@enduml
